-- Wal-Mart Workers' Gender Bias Back-Pay Case Class Certification Upheld
-- Karen Gullo
-- 2010-04-26T17:10:20Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-04-26/wal-mart-employee-gender-bias-class-action-upheld-by-u-s-appeals-court.html

          
          
             Wal-Mart Stores Inc. workers suing
over gender bias won a federal appeals court ruling upholding
class certification of their claims for back pay, according to
court records.  
